title: Dolphins coach Joe Philbin fired four games into his fourth season
text:
Home › Pro Sports › Dolphins coach Joe Philbin fired four games into his fourth season Dolphins coach Joe Philbin fired four games into his fourth season Advertising Widget  27 a.m. 
MIAMI (AP) — New Miami Dolphins coach Dan Campbell believes his underachieving team needs to show more aggressiveness that stops just short of dirty play, and he looks forward to breaking up a few fights in practice.
